OL,5, The number of prison officers in       
OL,6, England and Wales who took sick days   
OL,7, for mental health reasons nearly       
OL,8, doubled over five years.               
OL,10,FStaff taking time off rose from 1,456  
OL,11,Fin 2016/17 to 2,879 in 2021/22,        
OL,12,FMinistry of Justice data obtained by   
OL,13,FBBC Radio Kent shows.                  
OL,15,FThe Prison Officers' Association (POA) 
OL,16,Fsays long hours, violence and poor pay 
OL,17,Fare causing staff burnout.             
OL,19,FThe government says it is providing    
OL,20,Fextensive mental health support.       
